						<img src="../img/English/credit_help_log/001.jpg" id="steps">	
					</td>
				</tr>				
				<tr>
					<td id="steps_tab_explain">
						<ul>
							<li>
								<b>Configs database exists :</b> checks if the configuration file exists.
							</li>
							<li>
								<b>Test to open a configuration :</b> checks if it's possible to open a configuration (if is not possible 
								the default settings will restored).
							</li>
							<li>
								<b>Materials database exists :</b> checks if the database exists.
							</li>
							<li>
								<b>Globals :</b> the ShaderTools will check several things (they are represented by sub section that 
								we recognize through different tabs).
							</li>
							<li>
								<b>import :</b> it checked that the Python libraries are correctly imported.
							</li>
							<li>
								<b>database exists :</b> checks if Test table exists.
							</li>
							<li>
								<b>insert into database :</b> insert test datas inside Test table.
							</li>
							<li>
								<b>select in database :</b> test if it is possible to query the database.
							</li>
							<li>
								<b>update into database :</b> update Test table.
							</li>
							<li>
								<b>default configuration verification :</b> test if it's possible to load the default settings.
							</li>
							<li>
								<b>check folders :</b> checks if the folders and subfolders are properly initialized. 
							</li>
							<li>
								<b>workbase :</b> checks if workbase file exists.
							</li>
							<li>
								<b>help :</b> check if 'help' file backup exists.
							</li>
							<li>
								<b>img :</b> check if 'img' file backup exists.
							</li>
							<li>
								<b>bookmark import :</b> checks the Python libraries inside 'bookmark' file are correctly created.
							</li>
							<li>
								<b>bookmark save :</b> checks if 'bookmark' copy is correctly created before to update current bookmark file. 
							</li>
							<li>
								<b>bookmark folder :</b> checks if the materials folder is correctly created.
							</li>
							<li>
								<b>bookmark update :</b> updates the bookmark file.
							</li>
							<li>
								<b>Panel :</b> checks if the user interface contains no errors.
							</li>
						</ul>						
					</td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td id="steps_tab_title">
